HEADWORD: Curio
<hw>Cu"ri*o</hw> <pr>(k?"r?-?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Curios</plw> <pr>(-<?/z)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Abbreviation of
